<paragraph id="A8C1589672F90FD97A20974DA787A588" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Habit and habitat.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="534468B867D3A23B427E48AE5B237C00" pageId="0" pageNumber="79">Scattered to gregarious on the ground covered with dead and decaying leaves of broadleaf forest, from summer to autumn.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
